# Language Statistics Configuration
# Prioritize Go in GitHub language stats

# Treat frontend as secondary (optional - uncomment if you want to de-emphasize Svelte)
# *.svelte linguist-documentation
# web/**/*.js linguist-documentation
# web/**/*.css linguist-documentation

# Mark generated/binary files
*.mod linguist-generated
*.sum linguist-generated
traffic-sim linguist-vendored
*.exe linguist-vendored

# Ensure Go files are counted
*.go linguist-language=Go

# Documentation doesn't count towards stats
*.md linguist-documentation
LICENSE linguist-documentation
